      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical R2023 R1 used under validated installation; regression test suite executed and passed prior to simulation campaign. Version-controlled input decks archived in FDA OSEL repository.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms (FDA in-house code, Ansys, DePuy Synthes internal solver) operate under documented SQA plans. Ansys R2023 R1 regression suite passed with zero failures. FDA code version 4.2.1 is formally validated per 21 CFR Part 11 controls. Gradation 2 achieved and matches required level for Medium model risk."
