      "rationale": "Three meshes (55k, 220k, 880k elements) used. GCI for stiffness QoI: 0.41%; yield force QoI: 0.63%; force at 40 mm: 0.58%. All GCI values well below 1% threshold. Achieved level exceeds required level, providing additional confidence margin."
